Author: secretweightloss
Text: I ended up caving and ordering the pizza. I ate like half a pizza and 14 chicken strips and I don’t even like meat and I’m usually vegetarian. I’ve still got half a pizza at home now and I wanna throw it out but I hate wasting things :/

Author: Blue_Wave92
Text: Oh no! Hope you feel better!! Bring sick is no fun. If you're stomach is empty, maybe try some whole foods like a veggie and pasta or rice and beans dish?? Something ago but lighter? Pizzas equals regret :(
